item.dc:creator: @java_is_my_bitch1 java is my bitch.
item.description:
@java_is_my_bitch1 wrote:

[quote=“satesql, post:6, topic:252072”]Personally I’m very simplistic, and all those music, tabs, multi color themes… IDS FOR CFG FILES, which btw, why would someone on the server need these, and I’m not talking about staff? It’s too much imo… If you wanna play some music, use media player or some other player, ADDING all that stuff is gonna increase memory usages by far… It’s great your creating Jframes, and GUI but just seems too much… I have an idea, fix the logging part like make the logging interface transparent so you can see your background of the client…[/quote]Actully…I agree…I’m going to remove some of the Jframe.
